{"tid":2398142,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有無又平又好用嘅剪片軟件？","createTime":"2021-02-07T04:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T13:01:01.000Z","uid":349913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2f33140cf6ae3e2ccfe4195b237ad25c6db38627","tid":2398142,"uid":349913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:56:43.000Z","msg":"有無咩又平又好用嘅剪片軟件可以推介？<br />\n<br />\n因為我發覺我用filmora剪片，當我將個file拖過去我個project到嘅時候， 係另一部電腦開嗰陣時，成日都file missing ( 明明都已經save咗喺同一個外置harddisk度)<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgLfLFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkgLfLFY.jpg&h=0bb40f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvB297f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvB297f.jpg&h=92b8dda1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想問有冇啲咩剪片software可以解除到呢個限制？<br />\n即係總之個file拖到去個project嗰度嘅時候， 個file就係project嗰度， 唔需要再乜嘢relocate啲file 或者一定連住嗰啲file， 咁我隨時都可以delete啲file都ok&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"a39ed88fc8aacb4fbe4082369b80b47add608a63","tid":2398142,"uid":391202,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5ffbe906ed25b7c9e169b086a0e95b9a7d1f034","tid":2398142,"uid":295230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:04:21.000Z","msg":"DaVinci Resolve<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔剪4k 免費版夠用有餘"},{"pid":"c4f8000c2fc01445ac099f45873a4d7e038176b5","tid":2398142,"uid":101481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"支那萬興喵影"},{"pid":"fad92b4f87e3024d3fb6a42a7751fef0da5671f7","tid":2398142,"uid":2959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"iMovie <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b41a961c50bb991a2f9cbb70f1b390bb2af3b1","tid":2398142,"uid":366509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:52:51.000